      "comment": "PECO (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.5 lengths away in third (30.29) behind Highgate Pete at Launceston. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can measure up this time. SET ALIGHT (5) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by one length at Launceston in a handy 30.29 beating Grapefruit Racer. Leading player again. SET THE TONE (3) was sent out big odds last time but scored an upset win in a Other at Launceston (16.29). Must be included in calculations. STARDUST LAD (4) is worth including.",
